$interpreted: Sharice: (S-So they really only intended to apply ointments and nothing more?)
Sharice: (Neck doesn't hurt as much, that's for sure......)
Yan-Bo: With treatment and proper rest, in few days, worry no more, be no sore.
Sharice: Hmph. My body naturally heals fast. Nothing to do with those herbs of yours!
Yan-Bo: Understand, I do. Not move, lay and rest, you will.

Yan-Bo: Pang, used all healing herbs, I have.
Have a walk and pick some with me,  you can?
Pang: Understood. I shall accompany Master on this trip.
Sharice: (These monstrosities aren't as bad as I previously made them out to be after all......)
Sharice: Wow, such breathtaking beauty...
Sharice: What am I doing? No one in sight; now is the perfect time to make a getaway!
Sharice: What a lovely place. Once I report back to the boss, the whole team will be credited for discovering this land and the nobles will surely be satisfied!
Sharice: Huff puff~ This should be far enough. Just a bit further and I'll make it to our troops' rendezvous...
Puggi: Sweet Sharice, what are you doing here~?
Puggi: Oh, oh, oh wait, I know! You came to play with me, right? Has your neck healed already?
Sharice: Tch, didn't think I'd cross paths with you here, but I won't complain!
Sharice: You are to blame for putting me in such a predicament!
Sharice: You look nice and plump. I'll slice you in half, roast one side and fry the other! Winner winner, chicken dinner for me!
Sharice: That's the price you'll pay for embarrassing me!
Puggi: Hold up, now wait a minute. I didn't mean to hurt you! It's all Pang's fault! If you want justice, take it up with him, not me!
Puggi: AHHHHHHHH!!!
Sharice: Listen up, fat bird, you better shut your damn mouth or I'm going to make sure you have a place on tonight's menu!
Hestia: What are you doing to Puggi!?

Hestia: You ill-mannered bully! All of us keep you here
to treat your wounds, and this is how you repay our kindness?
Sharice: You're the ones who bullied me! I didn't ask for any of your help in the first place! This chicken here ain't gonna make it to next spring either!
Hestia: Screw you! I won't allow you to do that!
Sharice: You are indeed one ugly and freaky fish, yet you ain't too shabby a fighter!
Hestia: Shut it, you're the one that's ugly and freaky!
Yan-Bo: Now now, that's quite enough.
Pang: Sharice? Didn't we instruct you to recuperate on the Lake Island?
Sharice: I was fully healed long ago. No need to waste my time on that stinkin island!
Puggi: Healed that fast? Good to hear, sassy Sharice! Congratz!
Sharice: AHH!!!
Sharice: Ow ow owwie, my neck......
Puggi: What, why are you looking at me? She said she was good to go!
Pang: Seems like, need a few more days to recover.
Sharice: No good, if I don't make my leave in time, my team......
Pang: Team?
Sharice: (Crap, can't reveal my status nor purpose here, otherwise my cover is going to be blown......)
Sharice: No, nothing!

Yan-Bo: Well, if so say, return to recover once more.
Need few days more for you to heal; take great fall, you did.
Hestia: This ungrateful human has brought us nothing but trouble. Leave her be! Our hospitality ends here!

Yan-Bo: Sharice and Karnulla, in my eyes, the same.
Sweet, simply children, they are.
Puggi: That's right! Although sweet Sharice here doesn't have the best personality around...
Puggi: Everything else about her is cute and adorable~
Pang: A rare instance, but I have to admit, you got a point there.
Sharice: Cut it out, I'm neither cute nor adorable...don't look at me like that!
